## Important
- Match events by date/time AND subject similarity (e.g. "Meeting with X" in email matches "Sync with X" on the calendar).
- When updating, **append** to the existing description — never overwrite it.
- For new events, extract the best start/end times from the email. If only a date is mentioned with no time, default to a 30-minute event at 9:00 AM in the user's timezone.
- Use ISO 8601 format for start/end times (e.g. "2026-03-05T09:00:00-05:00").

